%h1 Activate your account

%p You should shortly receive a text message containing an activation code. Enter that five digit number below to confirm that your phone number belongs to you. 
%p Then, you'll be signed up to Bukkit - and can start SMSing to-do items!

= form_tag(activations_path, :method => :post, :class => "horizontal-form") do |f|
  .control-group
    %label.control-label Authorization code
    .controls
      = hidden_field_tag :return_url, @return_url
      = hidden_field_tag :phone_number, @account.phone_number
      = text_field_tag :activation_code
  .control-group
    = submit_tag "Activate"
